Title: Series: Salvatoris Beatae Mariae Virginis Sanctorum Apostolorum Icones
Series: Les Grands Apôtres
Description: Virgin standing whole-length in landscape, facing front, with hands joined; in the background, representations of return from Egypt on the right and of the Assumption on the left; copy after Callot without the halo Etching
Curator's comments: For the original set of sixteen plates, see 1861,0713.193.
Bibliographic references: Meaume 1860 / Recherches sur la vie et les ouvrages de Jacques Callot (106) (copy)
